          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "I’ve spent a lot of my life reporting on corruption, and we at TMI are able to do this kind of work because of our supporting subscribers (please ",
            "type": "text",
